room_title: Escape room "Tick Tok" by Panic Room CT in Stamford
room_description: Join your extended family in celebrating the life of your eccentric uncle Vladimir Vostok, a wealthy and reclusive hedge fund manager. Uncle Tok, as you affectionately called him, has invited you to participate in the reading of his last will and testament, with a challenging twist! Do you have what it takes to stake your claim to a share of his fortune?
